    <p>Born in September 2007, <strong>Nerdstore</strong> was created based on the passion of its
        founders and their legion of fans for the most diverse nerd related themes. Ranging from comics, fantasy and
        RPG, they wanted to,
        somehow, express the pride of being part of <strong>NERDPOWER</strong>!</p>
    <p>A force that was asleep until then, but that exploded and now dominates several segments of POP Culture.
        From the blockbusters of cinema with our superheroes, or best-selling books with dragons and magical
        warriors to the game industry with events and millionaire championships that attract millions of viewers
        worldwide.</p>
